commentary: Denly to Balbirnie, 1 wide, OUT fired w-a-a-a-y down the leg side, but Foakes is very excited about the stumping! That is a hell of a way to make your case on ODI debut!

Kumar Dharmasena is unsure, goes for a chat with square leg, then calls for the TV umpire. Soft signal is not out, by the way. There's definitely some glove on the ball, but looks like it bounced into the glove; yep, that's what Aleem Dar is saying.
